<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Passport to Lifetime Fitness</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <style>
        body         { padding-top:80px; word-wrap:break-word; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="page-header text-center">
        <h1><span class="fa fa-heart-o"></span> Passport to Lifetime Fitness</h1>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">Logout</a>
        <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">My Profile</a>
    </div>
    <form action="/form" method="POST">
        
        <br>
        Please select the activity you participated in today: 
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="activitylist" value="basketball"/>Basketball
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="activitylist" value="yoga"/>Yoga
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="activitylist" value="swimming"/>Swimming
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="activitylist" value="martial arts"/>Martial Arts
            </label>
        <br>
        <br>
        <h2>PREÂ­SESSION:</h2>
            This section refers to how you were feeling before <span class="activity">activity</span>.
        <br>
        <br>
        Today, I felt: 
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="presession" value="great"/>Great
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="presession" value="good"/>Good
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="presession" value="ok"/>OK
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="presession" value="ill"/>Ill
            </label>
        <br>
        Overall, I feel that my health is: 
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="health" value="verygood"/>Very good
        </label>
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="health" value="good"/>Good
        </label>
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="health" value="bad"/>Bad
        </label>
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="health" value="verybad"/>Very bad
        </label>
    <br>
    <br>
    <h2>POSTSESSION:</h2>
        This section refers to how you felt after <span class="activity">activity</span>:
    <br>
    The BEST part of activity was:<br>
    <input type="text" name="bestpart">
    <br>
    The WORST part of activity was:<br>
    <input type="text" name="worstpart">
    <br>
    <br>
    After participating in <span class="activity">activity</span>, I would do <span class="activity">activity</span> on my own.
    <br>
    <label>
            <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="verygood"/>Strongly Agree
        </label>
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="good"/>Agree
        </label>
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="bad"/>Disagree
        </label>
        <label>
            <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="verybad"/>Strongly Disagree
        </label>
    <br>   
    <br>
    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    <br>
    <br>
    <h3>Thank you for completing the Passport to Lifetime Fitness!</h3>
    <br>
    </form>
      
       

    <div class="text-center">
        <p>A demo by <a href="http://scotch.io">Scotch</a>.</p>
        <p>Visit the <a href="http://scotch.io/tutorials/javascript/easy-node-authentication-setup-and-local">tutorial</a>.</p>
    </div>

</div>
<footer>
        <% include includes/footer.ejs %>    
</footer>
</body>

